The TITANS are back! After a hellish confrontation with Slade Wilson, our heroes are met with a new foe in the mysterious Red Hood, who claims he's trying to liberate Gotham City. Even worse, the sadistic and manipulative Jonathan Crane is on the loose, hoping to get payback after being foiled by the Dynamic Duo some time ago. Can our heroes stop moping long enough to stop the threats in their city? Check out this full Titans S3 spoiler-filled review to find out!

